content.rendered: Hi lovers!! This video is how to make Cauliflower fried rice! I’ve posted this meal on my snap and instagram before, as it’s one of my ALL time favs, so I thought I’d make an actual step by step recipe video on it for you all! It’s kinda long… but all these steps are important so if you wanna try it make sure ya watch!! You can totally add other veggies you have in this as well. Peppers, zucchini, cabbage, etc., anything you usually like in your fried rice:) I hope you all enjoy this video, and PLEASE let me know what you think if you like it!
